oclaim all these words in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem: ‘Obey the words of this covenant and carry them out.’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I strongly warned your ancestors when I brought them out of the land of Egypt until today, warning them time and time again, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit today, rising early and warning"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 36:15","book":"2Ch","chapter":36,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:13","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:25","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 25:3","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 26:5","book":"Jer","chapter":26,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 29:19","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":19,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:33","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":33,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 35:14–15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":14,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 44:4","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":4,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" ‘Obey me.’ "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Ch 36:15","book":"2Ch","chapter":36,"verse":15},{"label":"Jr 7:13","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 7:25","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":25},{"label":"Jr 25:3","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 26:5","book":"Jer","chapter":26,"verse":5},{"label":"Jr 29:19","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 32:33","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":33},{"label":"Jr 35:14–15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 44:4","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit today, rising early and warning"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet they would not obey or pay attention; each one followed the stubbornness of his evil heart. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:24","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" So I brought on them all the curses of this covenant, because they had not done what I commanded them to do.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Jr 7:24","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":24},{"label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to me, “A conspiracy has been discovered among the men of Judah "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 22:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 6:9","book":"Hos","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the residents of Jerusalem. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 22:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":25},{"label":"Hs 6:9","book":"Hos","chapter":6,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They have returned to the iniquities of their ancestors "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:39","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:2","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 65:7","book":"Isa","chapter":65,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" who refused to obey my words and have followed other gods to worship them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 28:14","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 13:10","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" The house of Israel and the house of Judah broke my covenant I made with their ancestors."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 26:39","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":39},{"label":"Neh 9:2","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 65:7","book":"Isa","chapter":65,"verse":7},{"label":"Dt 28:14","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 13:10","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore, this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: I am about to bring on them disaster that they cannot escape. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 39:4–7","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 9:1–4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will cry out to me, but I will not hear them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 39:4–7","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4},{"label":"Am 9:1–4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the cities of Judah and the residents of Jerusalem will go and cry out to the gods they have been burning incense to, but they certainly will not save them in their time of disaster. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:35","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:35","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Your gods are indeed as numerous as your cities, Judah, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:28","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the altars you have set up to Shame "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Baal"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:24","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 9:10","book":"Hos","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" —altars to burn incense to Baal —as numerous as the streets of Jerusalem."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 2:28","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":28},{"label":"Jr 3:24","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":24},{"label":"Hs 9:10","book":"Hos","chapter":9,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Baal"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“As for you, do not pray for these people. Do not raise up a cry or a prayer on their behalf, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 14:11","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for I will not be listening when they call out to me at the time of their disaster."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16},{"label":"Jr 14:11","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What right does my beloved have"},{"kind":"text","text":" to be in my house, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:1–15","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" having carried out so many evil schemes?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Can holy meat "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= sacrificial meat"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hg 2:12","book":"Hag","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" prevent your disaster "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"LXX; MT reads meat pass from you"},{"kind":"text","text":" so you can celebrate?"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:1–15","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":1},{"label":"Hg 2:12","book":"Hag","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= sacrificial meat"},{"marker":2,"text":"LXX; MT reads meat pass from you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" named you"},{"kind":"text","text":" a flourishing olive tree, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 52:8","book":"Psa","chapter":52,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 128:3","book":"Psa","chapter":128,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 14:6","book":"Hos","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" beautiful with well-formed fruit."},{"kind":"text","text":" He has set fire to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and its branches are consumed "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Vg; MT reads broken"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the sound of a mighty tumult. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 1:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 52:8","book":"Psa","chapter":52,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 128:3","book":"Psa","chapter":128,"verse":3},{"label":"Hs 14:6","book":"Hos","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Ezk 31:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":12},{"label":"Ezk 1:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":1,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Vg; MT reads broken"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies who planted you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:2","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:7","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:21","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" has decreed disaster against you, because of the disaster "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or evil"},{"kind":"text","text":" the house of Israel and the house of Judah brought on themselves when they angered me by burning incense to Baal.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 5:2","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 5:7","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 2:21","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or evil"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" informed me, so I knew."},{"kind":"text","text":" Then you helped me to see their deeds,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"for I was like a docile "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or pet"},{"kind":"text","text":" lamb led to slaughter. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 44:11","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 44:22","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 53:7","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 12:3","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" I didn’t know that they had devised plots against me:"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Let’s destroy the tree with its fruit; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit bread"},{"kind":"text","text":" let’s cut him off from the land of the living "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 27:13","book":"Psa","chapter":27,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 53:8","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that his name will no longer be remembered.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 44:11","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":11},{"label":"Ps 44:22","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":22},{"label":"Is 53:7","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 12:3","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"Ps 27:13","book":"Psa","chapter":27,"verse":13},{"label":"Is 53:8","book":"Isa","chapte